<% page_title :home_index %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-padding-top-4">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl"><%= t('.title') %></h1>
    <p class="govuk-body">Use this service to find out what other jobs you can do with your current skills. You can also find out how to get new skills that could help you find a better job.</p>
    <%= link_to 'Start now', task_list_path, class: 'govuk-button govuk-button--start govuk-!-margin-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8', role: 'button' %>
    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">You'll get the most out of this service if all of the following apply to you:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>you're employed</li>
      <li>you don't have a degree</li>
      <li>you're based in the Manchester area</li>
      <li>you're aged 24 or over</li>
      <li>you're earning below £35,000 per year</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="govuk-body">If these don’t all apply to you, try visiting the <%= link_to 'National Careers Service', 'https://nationalcareers.service.gov.uk/', class: 'govuk-link', target: '_blank' %> or your local <%= link_to 'Jobcentre Plus', 'https://www.jobcentreplusoffices.com/', class: 'govuk-link', target: '_blank' %> instead.</p>
  </div>
</div>
